{"id": "23384", "post": "<div class=\"post-23384 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-editorial tag-community-news tag-improvements tag-news tag-provider-table-layout\" id=\"post-23384\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/improved-provider-table-layout-lowendbox/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Improved Provider Table Layout @ LowEndBox</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/community-news/\" rel=\"tag\">community news</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/improvements/\" rel=\"tag\">improvements</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/news/\" rel=\"tag\">news</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/provider-table-layout/\" rel=\"tag\">provider table layout</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> June 12, 2020 @ 12:00 pm, by Jon Biloh</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/leb-banner-300x169.png.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"screenshot litespeed-loaded\" title=\"Improved Table Layout for VPS Providers\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/leb-banner-300x169.png.webp\" alt=\"Improved Table Layout for VPS Providers\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></a></p><p>As part of our continued efforts to improve all aspects of LowEndBox we have made improvements to our top-of-page table which provides categories and tags for the offers we publish.</p><p>The new layout includes a refreshed list of top locations along with the addition of \u201cSpecializations\u201d for new, in-demand, features such as DDoS Protection, High CPU (Ryzen type CPUs), NVMe Storage, etc. A thanks goes to all the members on LowEndTalk who offered their opinion on <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/164020/which-leb-specialization-group-is-least-most-interesting\">what we should change</a>.</p><p>We\u2019ve also added links to additional content such as:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/best-cheap-vps-hosting-updated-2020/\">Best VPS Providers 2020 @ LowEndBox</a></li><li><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/2019-best-vps-provider-as-voted-by-the-low-end-talk-community/\">Best VPS Providers 2019 @ LowEndTalk</a></li><li><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/best-los-angeles-vps-providers/\">Best Cheap Los Angeles VPS Providers</a></li></ul><p>Our eventual goal is to create landing pages for every specialization that provides more information (explanations) on each topic along with all of the associated offers and content.</p><p>We will continue to tweak and make improvements as time permits.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Improved-table-layout-providers-2.jpg.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-23388 litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Improved-table-layout-providers-2.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"759\" height=\"236\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Improved-table-layout-providers-2.jpg.webp 926w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Improved-table-layout-providers-2-300x93.jpg.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Improved-table-layout-providers-2-768x239.jpg.webp 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 759px) 100vw, 759px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 759px) 100vw, 759px\" srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Improved-table-layout-providers-2.jpg.webp 926w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Improved-table-layout-providers-2-300x93.jpg.webp 300w, https://lowen